---

<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 to-white overflow-hidden py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 relative z-10">
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-start text-left">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-700 text-sm font-extrabold mb-6 animate-pulse">
        ¡SÓLO POR HOY 70% DE DESCUENTO!
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6">
        Crea Mascotas <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-accent">Amigurumi</span> Irresistibles
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-lg leading-relaxed">
        Descarga al instante más de <span class="font-bold text-primary-600">60 patrones exclusivos en español</span>. Ideal para tejer, regalar o iniciar tu propio negocio desde casa.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto">
        <a 
          href="/ebook-patrones-mascotas" 
          class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white bg-primary-600 rounded-full hover:bg-primary-700 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-primary-500/30 transform hover:-translate-y-1"
        >
          Ver Oferta a $8 USD
        </a>
        <a 
          href="#beneficios" 
          class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-slate-700 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-full hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all shadow-sm"
        >
          Saber Más
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500">
        <div class="flex -space-x-2">
          <!-- Placeholder avatars -->
          <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=1" alt="Usuario" />
          <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=5" alt="Usuario" />
          <img class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full border-2 border-white" src="https://i.pravatar.cc/100?img=9" alt="Usuario" />
        </div>
        <p>Más de <span class="font-bold text-slate-700">1,000+ tejedoras</span> ya empezaron.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="md:w-1/2 relative w-full aspect-square md:aspect-auto md:h-[600px] flex justify-center items-center">
      <!-- Decoración de fondo -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-primary-200 to-secondary-200 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-30 transform scale-90 animate-pulse"></div>
      
      <!-- Placeholder de la imagen principal -->
      <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-md bg-white p-4 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border border-white/50 rotate-3 transition-transform hover:rotate-0 duration-500">
        <img 
          src="/images/hero-placeholder.webp" 
          alt="Perro amigurumi tejido a crochet" 
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl object-cover bg-slate-100"
          style="aspect-ratio: 4/5;"
          onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20width%3D%22400%22%20height%3D%22500%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%20400%20500%22%3E%3Crect%20fill%3D%22%23fce7f3%22%20width%3D%22400%22%20height%3D%22500%22%2F%3E%3Ctext%20fill%3D%22%23db2777%22%20font-family%3D%22sans-serif%22%20font-size%3D%2224%22%20dy%3D%2210.5%22%20font-weight%3D%22bold%22%20x%3D%2250%25%22%20y%3D%2250%25%22%20text-anchor%3D%22middle%22%3EImagen%20Amigurumi%3C%2Ftext%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E'"
        />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-white p-4 rounded-2xl shadow-xl flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="bg-secondary-100 p-2 rounded-full text-secondary-600">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">Patrones en Español</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Paso a paso</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
